 />\n2.  小支眼用生理鹽水<br />\n3.  2寸或3寸繃帶<br />\n4&middot;  三角巾<br />\n5.  敷料<br />\n6.  噴霧膠布（雖然唔係正常急救要救嘅用品 但好有用）<br />\n7.   哮喘藥<br />\n8.   紗布Gauze/廚房紙巾<br />\n9.   一次性冰包<br />\n10.  醫療手套<br />\n11.   水(枝裝細水/中水，唔好俾幾公斤嗰啲)(若許可，請連紙箱📦包裝)<br />\n12.   小林退熱貼<br />\n13.   牛皮膠紙<br />\n14.   吊鹽水嗰隻生理鹽水(交俾FA站)<br />\n<br />\n防具🥋<br />\n15.  頭盔<br />\n16.  眼罩<br />\n17.  口罩（n95 r95 普通款）<br />\n18.   電池 （2A +3A)<br />\n19.   索帶<br />\n20.   保鮮紙<br />\n21.  長遮<br />\n22.   洗con水/洗眼水<br />\n<br />\n❎唔要<br />\n消毒酒精（急救唔會用架 痛死人咩！！！！）<br />\n攻擊性武器(刀，士巴拿，棍，鐵枝等等)<br />\n勞工手套 (要買買3m)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n18區嘅物資存放點同時間<br />\n全部暫時待定<br />\n有最新消息會通知各位<br />\n未開設物資收集站前，麻煩各位可以放住係自己屋企先<br />\n<br />\n18區聯合群Link: <a href=\"https://t.me/UnitedHK18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUnitedHK18&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=52483ab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/UnitedHK18</a>"},{"pid":"776579924666c821756eeb90ffa7c09ab6d37cd2","tid":1332361,"uid":247187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3663f11e69f184a52af0ca791d67f7b43dfe6f","tid":1332361,"uid":247187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b7cba46dbdbcd9453b91fb93649f092eea8c0f","tid":1332361,"uid":280153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:50:54.000Z","msg":"巴打有心<br />\n推"},{"pid":"9291e4cec36341553c0af1e0bc02602d5704a73e","tid":1332361,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"003108b976ccd20177da694112841b662231e39c","tid":1332361,"uid":88823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT